Author: Rucknium [cre, aut, cph] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5999-8950>),
    Bernhard Pfaff [aut, cph] (Creator of rbtc, the package that rbch is originally based on.)
Maintainer: Rucknium <Rucknium@protonmail.com>
Description: Implementation of the RPC-JSON API for Bitcoin Cash (BCH) and
    utility functions for address creation and content analysis of its
    blockchain.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/Rucknium/rbch, https://www.bitcoinunlimited.info
